# Blinkit Sales Analysis – Business Requirements

## KPIs to Track
- Total Sales – Overall revenue generated from all items sold  
- Average Sales – Average revenue per sale  
- Number of Items – Total count of different items sold  
- Average Rating – Average customer rating for items sold  

---

## Problem Statements

Q1. Analyze Total Sales by Fat Content (Donut Chart)  
Q2. Analyze Total Sales by Item Type (Bar Chart)  
Q3. Compare Fat Content by Outlet for Total Sales (Stacked Column Chart)  
Q4. Evaluate Total Sales by Outlet Establishment (Line Chart)  
Q5. Analyze Sales by Outlet Size (Donut / Pie Chart)  
Q6. Assess Sales by Outlet Location (Funnel Map)  
